00:29:46,420 --> 00:29:51,500
UPSTAIRS HERE, FOOT HEALTH, PERM

381
00:30:00,360 --> 00:30:01,740
I rented it to him dirt cheap.

382
00:30:09,820 --> 00:30:11,060
Honestly,

383
00:30:11,680 --> 00:30:12,640
