421
00:37:26,660 --> 00:37:28,140
Vincent.

422
00:37:28,180 --> 00:37:29,620
You didn't come to the moon,

423
00:37:29,660 --> 00:37:31,420
the moon came to you.

424
00:37:32,080 --> 00:37:34,180
Lay off those late-night dramas.

425
00:38:19,120 --> 00:38:20,680
You idiot!

426
00:38:20,720 --> 00:38:22,100
What’s gotten into you?

427
00:38:22,140 --> 00:38:23,580
Why did you let her into my room?

428
00:38:23,620 --> 00:38:24,460
<i>Vincent.</i>

429
00:38:24,500 --> 00:38:26,140
Why swear at me in Cantonese?

430
00:38:26,660 --> 00:38:28,880
Afraid that miss might
understand your swearing?

431
00:38:29,900 --> 00:38:30,960
Hey asshole,

432
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:32,360
All those girls I turned down for you.

433
00:38:32,400 --> 00:38:33,340
You have never thanked me.

434
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:34,860
Now you yell at me

435
00:38:34,900 --> 00:38:36,340
for letting one in.

436
00:38:36,380 --> 00:38:37,380
I didn't do it randomly.

437
00:38:37,420 --> 00:38:38,860
I’ve seen her photos

438
00:38:38,900 --> 00:38:39,820
all over

439
00:38:39,860 --> 00:38:42,240
- your room!
- Shut up!

440
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:44,860
<i>Guilty conscience.</i>

441
00:38:44,900 --> 00:38:46,060
<i>Hey Vincent.</i>

442
00:38:47,080 --> 00:38:48,500
That little sister is here?

443
00:38:48,540 --> 00:38:49,820
Really?

444
00:38:49,860 --> 00:38:53,900
Vincent, Love-Struck Saber!

445
00:38:53,940 --> 00:38:54,800
Brother Han.

446
00:38:55,580 --> 00:38:56,420
You didn't tell me.

447
00:38:56,460 --> 00:38:58,760
- Shut up!
- It's none of your business!

448
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:02,820
<i>He has closed the door!</i>

449
00:39:02,860 --> 00:39:04,760
<i>The door was closed.</i>

450
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:06,360
<i>Let's leave them.</i>

451
00:39:15,260 --> 00:39:16,220
Jiang Qiaoxi.

452
00:39:21,040 --> 00:39:22,140
Is it you?

453
00:39:39,320 --> 00:39:40,280
The elevator's broken out here.

454
00:39:42,640 --> 00:39:44,460
You’ll have to crash at my place tonight.

455
00:39:44,500 --> 00:39:46,040
I’ll bunk over at Han Yin’s.

456
00:39:46,080 --> 00:39:47,320
Tomorrow, I'll grab a meal with you

457
00:39:47,360 --> 00:39:48,400
before you fly out.

458
00:39:53,060 --> 00:39:54,080
I didn't come to Hong Kong

459
00:39:54,120 --> 00:39:55,540
just to have one meal with you.

460
00:39:58,300 --> 00:39:59,540
Alright then,

461
00:39:59,580 --> 00:40:01,720
stay in Hong Kong a few more days.

462
00:40:01,760 --> 00:40:02,780
I’ll book you a hotel.

463
00:40:03,320 --> 00:40:05,360
You’d love Disneyland or Ocean Park,

464
00:40:05,960 --> 00:40:06,920
trust me.

465
00:40:07,420 --> 00:40:08,560
I don't want Disney.

466
00:40:09,700 --> 00:40:11,060
I didn’t come for Ocean Park, either.

467
00:40:11,900 --> 00:40:13,680
I came because you’re here.

468
00:40:14,740 --> 00:40:15,620
Jiang Qiaoxi.

469
00:40:17,900 --> 00:40:19,600
You're the one
who told me not to forget you.

470
00:40:25,980 --> 00:40:28,260
Yingtao, I’ve moved on with my life now.

471
00:40:29,780 --> 00:40:31,120
Does your new life

472
00:40:32,940 --> 00:40:33,980
include

473
00:40:34,020 --> 00:40:36,540
cutting off everyone from the past?

474
00:40:37,900 --> 00:40:40,000
And that includes me too, doesn’t it?

475
00:40:43,760 --> 00:40:44,720
Yes.

476
00:40:46,000 --> 00:40:47,560
I'm doing really well now,

477
00:40:49,820 --> 00:40:50,880
living my life

478
00:40:50,920 --> 00:40:51,880
with purpose.

479
00:40:52,680 --> 00:40:53,780
You should too, Yingtao.

480
00:40:53,820 --> 00:40:55,000
Then why did you

481
00:40:55,040 --> 00:40:56,660
talk about the future back then?

482
00:40:56,700 --> 00:40:58,580
Why did you ask me not to forget you?

483
00:40:58,620 --> 00:40:59,880
Then you just disappear

484
00:40:59,920 --> 00:41:01,600
- without a word?
- Because I don't need it.

485
00:41:01,640 --> 00:41:02,640
Yingtao, I just don’t.

486
00:41:02,680 --> 00:41:04,040
Don’t need what?

487
00:41:05,220 --> 00:41:07,380
You’re standing in a room full of me,

488
00:41:07,420 --> 00:41:09,380
saying that, you really think
that is convincing?

489
00:41:09,420 --> 00:41:10,380
Jiang Qiaoxi?

490
00:41:19,560 --> 00:41:20,560
Why do you always

491
00:41:20,600 --> 00:41:22,220
lock yourself away?

492
00:41:24,260 --> 00:41:25,300
The second something

493
00:41:25,340 --> 00:41:26,460
goes wrong,

494
00:41:27,540 --> 00:41:29,220
you just get into your own blind alley.

495
00:41:30,280 --> 00:41:31,800
Stuck in that narrow-minded bullshit.

496
00:41:33,280 --> 00:41:34,640
You make decisions alone

497
00:41:34,680 --> 00:41:35,880
and expect everyone

498
00:41:35,920 --> 00:41:37,440
to follow.

499
00:41:43,960 --> 00:41:45,960
I fought like hell to get here.

500
00:41:47,780 --> 00:41:48,740
I’m not leaving.

501
00:42:18,800 --> 00:42:19,760
Jiang Qiaoxi.

502
00:42:25,380 --> 00:42:27,340
I’ve had so many dreams,

503
00:42:28,760 --> 00:42:29,720
like in different

504
00:42:29,760 --> 00:42:31,220
parallel universes.

505
00:42:31,740 --> 00:42:33,620
There are so many versions of you.

506
00:42:35,780 --> 00:42:37,860
Every one of them ends differently.

507
00:42:44,240 --> 00:42:45,960
Even you from other universes

508
00:42:48,860 --> 00:42:50,180
would never picture me

509
00:42:52,360 --> 00:42:54,060
like what I am now.

